data.description: Welcome Home! Spacious and secluded Traditional home in Shohola, PA that is the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. When you enter this beautiful home you will be greeted by a stunning center hall staircase and immediately notice the soaring ceilings and natural light though-out. Situated on a generous 2.52 acre lot, this property boasts a three-bedroom layout with 2 1/2 baths, ensuring ample space for your family's needs.  The kitchen is a chef's dream with a five burner cooktop, double wall ovens, SS appliances, granite countertops and a Butcher Block Island. The Cherrywood cabinets gives you plenty of storage and Pantry.  The Living Room has Gorgeous hardwood floors, a stone front fireplace, vaulted ceilings and lots of windows. The Primary Bedroom is a true retreat with a WIC and en-suite with a beautifully tiled jacuzzi tub. There are two more large bedrooms and a full bath to finish off the second floor. Lower level is partially finished with a large Family room, work out area, lots of storage and sliders to the back yard. There is a two-car garage, central air and a whole house generator as well.   The property is private and surrounded by nature.  $600.00 a Year for road maintenace.  Schedule your showing today.
